      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "@sipa - what you talk about is indeed a better solution, but since no one seems interested in making those changes, then i still argue that my fix is better than doing nothing - and will benefit the network too IMHO as current much traffic is wasted on nodes sending and receiving duplicate blocks. I'm not aware that my patch can be exploited to cause any network splits - which would be a good reason for not implementing it.\n",
